      {
        q: "What is Carbon Peeling treatment?",
        a: "Carbon Peeling (also known as Hollywood Peeling or Carbon Laser) is an innovative skin rejuvenating and cleansing treatment. A special mask containing carbon particles is applied to the skin, then treated with an Nd:YAG laser. The laser vaporizes the carbon along with impurities while stimulating collagen production."
      },
      {
        q: "What skin problems is it recommended for?",
        a: "Carbon Peeling is ideal for: treating enlarged pores, oily and acne-prone skin, removing blackheads, uneven skin tone, fine lines, dull and lifeless skin, and pigmentation spots. It is suitable for almost all skin types."
      },
      {
        q: "Is the treatment painful?",
        a: "The treatment is painless. The laser causes a mild warmth and tingling sensation that most patients find pleasant. No anesthesia is required."
